Review_body:
Throw in equal parts:A young woman's puppy love for the hero;
Lovemaking in a room full of sleeping, mud-caked Soviet soldiers;
A love triangle;
A tyrannical Soviet commander;
A soft-spoken Nazi sniper;
A Soviet soldier whose teeth - all of them - are metal.Shake vigorously.
Strain.And you have tonight's cocktail, Garbage at the Gates
